OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMainly dry, but with low cloud
OL,6,Fin some coastal districts edging
OL,7,Fwestwards with time, perhaps producing
OL,8,Fa little light rain at times.
OL,9,FBrightest inland in the west, although
OL,10,Ftending to become cloudier here. Very
OL,11,Fwarm and humid. Light winds throughout.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRather cloudy during the
OL,14,Fevening, with the odd spot of rain
OL,15,Fpossible. Becoming drier as the night
OL,16,Fprogresses, with lengthier clear
OL,17,Fperiods developing in southern areas
OL,18,Flater. Very warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
